[14/10/2017 15:08:34] <font color="#ffffff">Then, we sing together.</font>
[14/10/2017 15:08:34] <font color="#ffffff">-OK.</font>
[14/10/2017 15:08:35] <font color="#ffffff">-Vamos a cantar juntos.</font>
[14/10/2017 15:08:41] <font color="#0000ff">Cuando calienta el sol</font>
[14/10/2017 15:08:41] <font color="#0000ff">aquí en la playa...</font>
[14/10/2017 15:08:48] <font color="#0000ff">...siento tu cuerpo vibrar</font>
